<subSubSection pageId="693" pageNumber="694" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="693" pageNumber="694">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="693" pageNumber="694">This species is found along the Coastal Plain and Piedmont Plateau from southeastern New York and New Jersey to northern Florida, west to southeastern Oklahoma and southeastern Texas [see Noonan 1991: Fig. 270]. The record from southwestern Ohio (Blatchley 1910: 186) is probably in error.</paragraph>
